{"tid":1818871,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中醫組織「國難忠醫」負責人 1 月 8 日廣州被帶走　母親指音訊全無","createTime":"2020-01-10T09:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T21:31:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"563cf495822eeadd52e2a1e9e8811b0eb08ebc1b","tid":1818871,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"反送中運動人道支援中醫組織「國難忠醫」負責人<br />\n1 月 8 日廣州被帶走　母親指音訊全無<br />\n<br />\n【記者會直播片段：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/39ZnD4T】\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39ZnD4T%E3%80%91&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=6b1e6ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/39ZnD4T】</a><br />\n<br />\n支援抗爭者組織「國難忠醫」在反送中運動期間一直提供中醫支援，其組織 Telegram 昨晚表示其中一名負責人「忠醫林鄭」在大陸被捕。另一負責人「細牛」（圖左）及「忠醫林鄭」母親（圖右）今午在立法會議員楊岳橋陪同下見記者，表示「忠醫林鄭」過去五年在廣州中醫藥大學修讀中醫，惟在 1 月 8 日凌晨在宿舍突然被拉走。<br />\n<br />\n「忠醫林鄭」及後突然在 Telegram 群組未經其他人同意下新增一名陌生人，該名陌生人至今未有發表任何言論。直至昨晚 8 時許，「忠醫林鄭」的房友主動聯絡「細牛」，向他表示「moning on live（意指在線監視）」、「ghost everywhere」、「don&rsquo;t tell anything via internet」等字句。直至今早，其房友再向 「細牛」表示，自己曾被扣留 24 小時並已獲釋，但「忠醫林鄭」但仍被行政拘留。<br />\n<br />\n「忠醫林鄭」的母親今午亦有會見記者，指兒子當日離開香港時為她治療腰痛，回廣州後便音訊全無。「細牛」強調，組織只是一心為提供人道支援，強調曾被醫治市民的資料不會被外泄，已有其他方法保存資料。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》稍後有更詳細報道。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1V5OrnA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1V5OrnA.jpg&h=8018986b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: 立場Facebook"},{"pid":"799c728f18bfad43f55d42b83c85994e22c011ef","tid":1818871,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:40:39.000Z","msg":"大撚鑊，唉<br />\n呢啲真係幫唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00749ebfaa070ffbc21de4bc4a616b1ab89982c","tid":1818871,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:40:52.000Z","msg":"佢中國讀書，唔好再屌人送中"},{"pid":"25d259a8454dbc002e35647f505dc59600f00159","tid":1818871,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"要屌就屌個實習制度"},{"pid":"19dcdf5acb181cd7d655b16795fbcd636cb50112","tid":1818871,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:43:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=7941584d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"0e3499c4d5dc773ccf0993ee4ae46ad18d8b7e21","tid":1818871,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a00749ebfaa070ffbc21de4bc4a616b1ab89982c","tid":1818871,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:40:52.000Z","msg":"佢中國讀書，唔好再屌人送中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:03:45.000Z","msg":"知更鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5563f745eb4ce9eddd491d3faa67ffd27ff41e0","tid":1818871,"uid":268927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25d259a8454dbc002e35647f505dc59600f00159","tid":1818871,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"要屌就屌個實習制度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T02:34:28.000Z","msg":"佢係係廣州讀中醫吧！看新聞稿咁講。好似話中大會比學生留係香港實習。我想講，除咗中醫,其實仲有其他科要到大陸實習。"},{"pid":"0289b2bdbb2b37ad3197db2864ba2c09fff76671","tid":1818871,"uid":258661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T21:31:55.000Z","msg":"北嫖"}]}